00:15:40,700 --> 00:15:41,340
No, I didn't.

297
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:41,740
Yes, you did.

298
00:15:42,180 --> 00:15:42,900
No, I didn't.

299
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:43,420
Wait a moment.

300
