334
00:17:11,820 --> 00:17:12,460
I just know it.

335
00:17:13,220 --> 00:17:14,900
Cai Yasi would never be so generous.

336
00:17:56,900 --> 00:17:57,580
How is Zhou Xiao?

337
00:17:58,820 --> 00:17:59,300
She is fine.

338
00:18:00,420 --> 00:18:01,420
They why are you here?

339
